@startuml
title Book Room - Activity Diagram

start

:Start Booking;
note right
Student initiates the room booking process from the Room Booking UI.
end note

:Display Progress;
note right
System shows booking progress or processing status to the student.
end note

:Send Booking Request;
note right
Room Booking UI sends bookRoom(requestDetails)
to RoomBookingController.
end note

:Verify Availability;
note right
RoomBookingController checks room availability using
AvailabilityCalendar (roomId, dates).
end note

if (Room Available?) then (Yes)
  :Reserve Room;
  note right
  System reserves the room for the selected dates.
  end note

  :Create Booking Record;
  note right
  System creates a booking record with studentId,
  roomId, and dates.
  end note

  :Return Booking Confirmation (Success);
  note right
  RoomBookingController returns successful booking confirmation
  to the Room Booking UI.
  end note
else (No)
  :Return Booking Status (Failure);
  note right
  System returns booking failure for unavailable room
  or date conflict.
  end note
endif

:Show Confirmation;
note right
Room Booking UI displays confirmation or an error message
to the student.
end note

stop
@enduml
